Object Account
  Has Name as String
  Private Has Pin as String

  Private Teach Reveal Pin using Self
    Pin of Self

  Teach Pin Length using Self
    Length of Use Reveal Pin of Self

  Teach Rename using Self and Fresh Name as String
    Change Name of Self to Fresh Name
    Name of Self

  Teach Label using Self returns String
    Name of Self

  Teach Describe With using Self and Prefix as String returns String
    "{Prefix}: {Name of Self}"

Object Premium Account extends Account
  Has Level as Int

  Teach Label using Self returns String
    "{Use Parent Label of Self} level {Level of Self}"

  Teach Describe With using Self and Prefix as String returns String
    "{Use Parent Describe With of Self with Prefix} level {Level of Self}"

Teach Welcome Account using Account Person as Account returns String
  Use Label of Account Person

Make Basic be New Account with Name be "Ada" and Pin be "secret"
Expect Use Pin Length of Basic is 6
Expect Use Rename of Basic with "Ada Lovelace" is "Ada Lovelace"
Expect Name of Basic is "Ada Lovelace"
Expect Use Label of Basic is "Ada Lovelace"
Expect Use Describe With of Basic with "Basic" is "Basic: Ada Lovelace"

Make Premium be New Premium Account with Name be "Grace" and Pin be "hidden" and Level be 2
Expect Use Pin Length of Premium is 6
Expect Use Label of Premium is "Grace level 2"
Expect Use Describe With of Premium with "VIP" is "VIP: Grace level 2"
Expect Use Welcome Account with Premium is "Grace level 2"
Change Name of Premium to "Grace Hopper"
Expect Name of Premium is "Grace Hopper"
